        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slot": "B",
      "title": "Honorific Interrogative",
      "pattern": "VERB + -시- + -아/어/여요? = Do you VERB? (honorific)",
      "meaning": "Do you VERB? (honorific)",
      "explanation": "* When -시- is combined with -아/어/여요, it becomes -셔요. Over time however, it changed to -세요 because it is easier to pronounce.",
      "examples": [
        {
          "korean": "살다 + -시- + -아/어/여요? → 사세요? = Do you live? (honorific)",
